{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStreamProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStreamProtocol\/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)-4wgh1"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO19InputStreamProtocolPAAE4read6buffer5count11cancellableSiSvSg_SiAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"read(buffer:count:cancellable:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"read","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"read","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"buffer"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is zero returns zero and does nothing. A value of "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"larger than ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On success, the number of bytes read into the buffer is returned."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. near the end of a file. Zero is returned on end of file"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(or if "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is zero),  but never otherwise.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The returned ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a nul-terminated string, it can contain nul bytes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"at any position, and this function doesn’t nul-terminate the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be returned. If an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"partial result will be returned, without an error."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On error -1 is returned and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set accordingly."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to read "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes from the stream into the buffer starting at"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"buffer","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Will block during this read.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/inputstreamprotocol\/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)-4wgh1"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/CancellableRef":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/cancellableref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GCancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" allows operations to be cancelled."}],"title":"CancellableRef"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/InputStreamProtocol/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)-4wgh1":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStreamProtocol\/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)-4wgh1","abstract":[{"type":"